                    <a class="section__back-to-top" href="#top"><i class="icon-font  icon-font--up-arrow"></i></a>
                    <p> We have rafts and equipment for up to 24 participants and can offer a number of great activities in the local area. The Goulburn River offers a short white water section suitable for a 2-3 hour introductory session and the Big River allows a great day trip on whitewater (in season). Rafts or inflatable canoes are the options of craft.</p>
                    <p>You can also have a very relaxing float down the Goulburn River where participants can learn the basics of guiding a raft and everyone has the leisure to bird watch or watch the scenery. Both the Big and the Goulburn Rivers provide an excellent venue for environmental studies.</p>
