                <section id="rogaining" class="section">
                    <h2 class="section__title">Rogaining</h2>
                    <a class="section__back-to-top" href="#top"><i class="icon-font  icon-font--up-arrow"></i></a>
                    <p>Rogaining is the sport of cross-country navigation; teams of two to five people visit as many checkpoints as they can in the time allowed. Traditionally, Rogaining is a 24 hour event, however, at Rubicon we typically run a 1 &frac12; to 2 &frac12; hour session either in bushland, farmland or around the Rubicon camp site. It is a great opportunity for students to challenge their navigation skills and learn how to find their way around using a map.</p>
